#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_lightgraffiti.xml:95
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"How much does the sum of all color channels <em>relative to the background "
"image</em> (<code>dR + dG + dB</code>) have to change until a pixel is "
"recognized as a light source?<br/>\n"
"            Raising this value might, in some cases, avoid that some light "
"objects lit by the light source are added to the light mask."
